''' Kodada Gudda ''' is well known pilgrimage place and temple located on a hill in [[Jagalur]] district of [[Karnataka]] in  [[South India|southern]], [[India]]. The temple at the top of the hill is dedicated to Lord Veerabhadhreshwara.

